Description of incident: Schwaab, Inc. notified customers of a data breach when DiscountRubberStamps.com (a Schwaab owned company) discovered unauthorized access in their computer system from January 22, 2014 through February 8, 2016. The information compromised may have included credit card information. For questions call 1-844-608-3819 or customers@discountrubberstamps.com More Information: http://oag.ca.gov/ecrime/databreach/reports/sb24-60906
